{
  "stem": "4700.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the citizen school, which was a lower grade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the children were expected to finish at 14 and go into the workforce or do, be apprenticed or something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to the academic school, but--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gymnasium, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did-- no, two years of the gymnasium, and then one or two years of the external.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'm not-- I think two years, probably.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were, again, very few Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was not a popular area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an area-- when my father and mother got married, it was a great housing shortage after the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was an area of a new blocks or flats were built.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they bought a-- what we'd call a unit--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--today.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not a fashionable area, it was on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not where the Jews normally lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there are very few Jews in the area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my husband in Vienna encountered a lot of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Czechs basically are not--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if the Jews speak with a German accent, they didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But for the Czech-speaking Jew, there was very little problem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did, at the-- before Hitler came, there was the protectorate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was very anti-Semitic already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was run by the fascists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were already anti-Jewish measures.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And various professional organizations already clamored for the Jews to be excluded-- the lawyers, the doctors, the shopkeepers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were already clamoring for the Jews to be excluded from the professions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, the association of high school students-- of not high school, university students, wanted numerous clauses for the Jews, because the Jews were in competition for them.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
